numericalExperiment.rationale: Ensemble of 10-year hindcasts and Predictions. Assess model skill in forecasting climate change on time-scales when the initial climate may exert some influence.
numericalExperiment.description: The atmospheric composition (and other conditions) should be prescribed as in the historical run (expt. 3.2) and the RCP4.5 scenario (expt. 4.1) of the long-term suite of experiments. Ocean initial conditions should be in some way representative of the observed anomalies or full fields for the start date. Land, sea-ice and atmosphere initial conditions are left to the discretion of each group.
